summary: All of you currently thirsting for Michael Sheen
body:
All of you currently thirsting for Michael Sheen

(Good choice by they way, he is a top bloke) could do yourselves a favour and see if his episode of celebrity bake off is available on line. The man is an absolute master at non creepy/sexual flirting. Seriously, it’s both a delight and an education.

They were standing next to each other looking down at a river or something and somehow they were … younger versions of themselves?
